    "causal_summary": "Add Ollama provider support to CocoIndex's embedder registry. Today CocoIndex's MANIFESTS is sbert-only; the config.py comment claims non-sbert names route via LiteLLM, but the path is unverified. This packet verifies that path or extends the loader, registers at least one Ollama embedder (e.g., ollama/nomic-embed-text), and smoke-tests end-to-end indexing + search.",
